   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-c" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Jake is rather suspicious.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-b" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I suspect Cedric.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-d" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You're the culprit, Leonard!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Upon investigation of the rosary you found, it seems that it is most likely ours. As this is a sensitive issue, please be mindful of your accusations. Now then, is there someone in particular that you suspect?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-b" image="QN_Npc_Cl_Fallen_Cedric.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-e" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Where is he now?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Hmm, I have also reached that very conclusion. The fact that he had been reducing the number of guards, along with the suspicious details regarding the ambush makes <FONT color=#a82424>Cedric</FONT> highly suspicious. We are currently tracking him down. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-c" image="QN_Jake.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-a" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I suppose...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Jake</FONT>? Hmm...Yes, I can see why you are suspicious. He's not around here now too. However, there is not enough evidence against him. I'll still keep an eye on him though.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-a" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Hmm… then…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>What?! You suspect ME? Hahaha, I think you've been watching Detective Conan too much. Be serious now, who is it that you really suspect?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-f" mid="30" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Don't worry.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Hmm, hang on. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Leonard quickly reads the report delivered to him by a messenger.)</FONT><BR>Bingo! <FONT color=#a82424>Frost Wind Forest</FONT>! A masked man was spotted heading there. Nab that little punk!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-2-f" image="QW_10.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Who would've thought that we would be betrayed by our own cleric...<BR>Please go to <FONT color=#a82424>Frost Wind Forest</FONT> now.</html>]]></talk_question>
